      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Consider customizing how your spells look when you can cast them. Your Quandrix spells might manifest amid kaleidoscopic swirls of fractal patterns, amplifying the tiniest movements of your somatic components. When your magic creates or alters creatures, it might briefly surround the targets with shimmering fractal designs or tessellated patterns."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "h1",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Building a Quandrix Character"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Any spellcasting class or subclass can work well for a Quandrix character. Both the scholarly focus of "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Wizards"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " (especially those who study the Schools of "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Abjuration"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ", "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Illusion"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ", or "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Transmutation"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ") and the metamagic manipulations of "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Sorcerers"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " are welcome in Quandrix, and many "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Druids"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " explore the patterns of nature in Quandrix as well. A few "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Clerics"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ", particularly those with the "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Knowledge"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " or "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Nature"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " domains, study in Quandrix as well."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Aside from traditional spellcasters, a few characters of other classes find homes in Quandrix. Some "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Fighters"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ", "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Monks"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ", "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Rangers"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ", and "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Rogues"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " study here, using Quandrix principles to train their minds."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "strong",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "em",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Suggested Characteristics."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " With subjects ranging from the physical and tangible to the paradoxical and strange, the student body of Quandrix College includes an eclectic mix of individuals. The Quandrix Personality Traits table suggests a variety of traits you might adopt for your character."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Quandrix Personality Traits"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "table",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "th",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "d6"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "th",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Personality Trait"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "1"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "When I find a subject I'm interested in, I won't stop studying until I know everything about it. It keeps me up at night."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "2"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "I hope this all makes sense to me one day. Until then, I'm going to keep faking it."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "3"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Equations and patterns come naturally to my mind. I wish friendship came just as easily."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "4"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "I believe I'm always the smartest person in the room. And I'll prove it, even if no one asks me to."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "5"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "If these classes have taught me anything, it's that reality is a lie, and nothing matters. So why bother?"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "6"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Before I graduate, I want to achieve something mathematically impossible. I must leave a legacy!"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
